Start symbols   S = {s1}
Final symbols   F = {s1}
Transitions
q0    inp   q1    out
s1    0     s2    
s1    1     s1    
s2    0     s1    
s2    1     s2    
Instantaneous description
remaining input        input: A*
current state          state: Q
}

